M|⛔ DE|tx|This folder (`ag-department/shared/brands/`) is no longer the source of truth for br context.
M|⛔ DE|**Mi|2026-05-15**
M|⛔ DE|Bran|
M|⛔ DE|tx|\| Old file \| Replaced by \|
M|⛔ DE|tx|\|----------\|------------\|
M|⛔ DE|tx|\| `brands/nz.md` \| `doc/vt/nz/br.md` + `CONTEXT.md` + `FEEDBACK.md` + `ds.md` \|
M|⛔ DE|tx|\| `brands/hb.md` \| `doc/vt/hb/br.md` + `CONTEXT.md` + `FEEDBACK.md` + `ds.md` \|
M|Why |tx|The old br stubs mixed short-term state (cg, open decisions) w/ long-term identity in a single file. When sn switched vt, stale context from the previous vt persisted in ag memory.
M|Why |tx|The new structure uses isolated, per-vt folders. mc reads the correct vt files fresh at sn start and injects scoped context using `[nz-*]` / `[hb-*]` prefixes.
M|What|**If|** Stop here. Load `doc/vt/[active]/` instead.
M|What|**If|** Edit `doc/vt/[name]/br.md` — not this folder.
M|What|tx|**dl these files?** Keep them as tombstones until nx curator run confirms all references are updated.